orrelated or not. We note that general\nMaxwellian Demons readily violate previously proposed, alternative such bounds,\nwhile the current bound still holds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2015 16:46:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2015 01:36:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 13 Sep 2015 17:50:16 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2015 00:57:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
